<!DOCTYPE html>  
<html lang="en">  
<head>  
    <meta charset="UTF-8">  
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">  
    <title>Pick Your Neighbor Block Party | 515 Buckroe Ave</title>  
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;600&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">  
    <style>  
        :root {  
            --ivory: #F7F4EF;  
            --gold: #C8A96B;  
            --black: #22201E;  
            --taupe: #CBBEAF;  
        }  
        body {  
            background-color: var(--ivory);  
            color: var(--black);  
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;  
            margin: 0;  
            padding: 0;  
            line-height: 1.6;  
        }  
        .container {  
            max-width: 900px;  
            margin: 0 auto;  
            padding: 40px 20px;  
            text-align: center;  
        }  
        .header {  
            margin-bottom: 50px;  
        }  
        .logo {  
            max-width: 180px;  
            margin-bottom: 20px;  
        }  
        h1 {  
            font-family: 'Cormorant+Garamond', serif;  
            font-size: 3.5rem;  
            font-weight: 400;  
            margin-bottom: 10px;  
            letter-spacing: 1px;  
        }  
        .hero-img {  
            width: 100%;  
            height: 500px;  
            background: url('https://images.zillowstatic.com/fp/370d6568c07e0c7a5237c569f417f7c8-full.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;  
            margin: 30px 0;  
            border: 1px solid var(--gold);  
        }  
        .gold-divider {  
            width: 60px;  
            height: 1px;  
            background-color: var(--gold);  
            margin: 20px auto;  
        }  
        .details {  
            font-size: 1.1rem;  
            margin: 40px 0;  
        }  
        .details h2 {  
            font-family: 'Cormorant+Garamond', serif;  
            font-size: 2rem;  
            color: var(--gold);  
        }  
        .features {  
            display: flex;  
            justify-content: space-around;  
            flex-wrap: wrap;  
            margin: 40px 0;  
            background: #fff;  
            padding: 30px;  
            border: 1px solid var(--taupe);  
        }  
        .feature-item {  
            flex: 1;  
            min-width: 200px;  
            padding: 10px;  
        }  
        .rsvp-form {  
            background: var(--black);  
            color: #fff;  
            padding: 50px;  
            margin-top: 50px;  
        }  
        .rsvp-form h3 {  
            font-family: 'Cormorant+Garamond', serif;  
            font-size: 2.2rem;  
            margin-bottom: 20px;  
        }  
        input {  
            width: 100%;  
            padding: 12px;  
            margin-bottom: 15px;  
            border: none;  
            background: var(--ivory);  
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;  
        }  
        button {  
            background: var(--gold);  
            color: var(--black);  
            padding: 15px 40px;  
            border: none;  
            font-weight: 600;  
            cursor: pointer;  
            text-transform: uppercase;  
            letter-spacing: 2px;  
            transition: 0.3s;  
        }  
        button:hover {  
            background: #b6985a;  
        }  
    </style>  
</head>  
<body>  
    <div class="container">  
        <div class="header">  
            <!-- Replace with your actual logo URL -->  
            <img src="YOUR_LOGO_URL_HERE" alt="Sherri Parsons Real Estate" class="logo">  
            <h1>Pick Your Neighbor</h1>  
            <div class="gold-divider"></div>  
            <p style="font-style: italic; font-size: 1.2rem;">Block Party & Private Luxury Tour</p>  
        </div>

        <div class="hero-img"></div>

        <div class="details">  
            <h2>Saturday, May 23rd | 11:00 AM — 2:00 PM</h2>  
            <p>515 Buckroe Ave, Hampton, VA</p>  
            <p>Join us for a beautiful afternoon by the beach. Bring a friend, meet the neighbors, and tour one of Buckroe’s newest luxury listings before it hits the market on June 1st.</p>  
        </div>

        <div class="features">  
            <div class="feature-item">  
                <p><strong>🍿 Popcorn Machine</strong></p>  
            </div>  
            <div class="feature-item">  
                <p><strong>🏰 Bounce House</strong></p>  
            </div>  
            <div class="feature-item">  
                <p><strong>🏠 Private Tours</strong></p>  
            </div>  
        </div>

        <div class="rsvp-form">  
            <h3>Will you be joining us?</h3>  
            <p>Please RSVP so we can ensure enough treats for everyone.</p>  
            <form>  
                <input type="text" placeholder="Full Name" required>  
                <input type="email" placeholder="Email Address" required>  
                <input type="tel" placeholder="Phone Number" required>  
                <button type="submit">RSVP Now</button>  
            </form>  
        </div>  
    </div>  
</body>  
</html>
